          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Daniel of Salach. The second volume of the Commentary of Daniel of Salach on the Psalms, comprising Pss. li. — c. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 1 items.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
              <relation name="dcterms:type" ref="http://purl.org/dc/terms/type" active="https://bl.syriac.uk/ms/535" passive="#theo-single">
